Airtel Nigeria Invests $600 Million in Expansion, ThisDay Says

-- B y   V i n c e n t   N w a n m a
-- 
2011-12-05T06:56:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-05/airtel-nigeria-invests-600-million-in-expansion-thisday-says.html
Airtel Nigeria Ltd., a unit of
 India ’s  Bharti Airtel Ltd. (BHARTI) , invested $600 million over the past
year to expand its network capacity and improve its service,
ThisDay  reported , citing Deepak Srivastava, the company’s chief
operating officer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
